    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Four new species of Meligethes Stephens from China and additional data on other species of the genus (Coleoptera: Nitidulidae: Meligethinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.259798> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.259798>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Male genitalia of Meligethes spp. 1 – 2: M. macrofemoratus sp. nov. (male paratype from China, Ningxia Hui Autonomous Region, Xixia Valley). 3 – 4: M. clinei Audisio, Sabatelli & Jelínek, 2015 (male holotype from China, Yunnan, Yulong Mts). 5 – 6: M. yak sp. nov. (male holotype from China, Sichuan, Maerkang). 7 – 8: M. nivalis Audisio, Sabatelli & Jelínek, 2015 (male paratype from China, Tibet, Yang Jing). Scale bar = 0.2 mm (Figs. 1 – 8)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/259798/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

